## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature up to October 2023, and new research may provide further insights into the topic. Additionally, while the studies reviewed provide substantial evidence of gender differences in pain perception, the exact biological and psychological mechanisms remain partially understood. Cultural and social factors influencing pain reporting and perception were not extensively covered in the available sources.

